WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'Lightnix' is a Workbench game played on an 8 by 8 tiles board,
where you click on tiles of various shapes, this will send
'lightning bolts' in 4 directions, horizontally and vertically.
If the lightning bolts hit identical tiles, those tiles will be
eliminated and you will get points according to the number of
removed tiles.

  If no tiles were eliminated, new tiles will appear randomly on
the board. Just remember to not let the game board fill up
completely as it would end the game.

  Have fun!

